---
import { CommunityMap } from "@/components/react/sections/CommunityMap";
---

<section id="map" class="border-t border-border">
  <div class="px-6 py-16 md:py-20 w-full mx-auto text-center">
    <p
      class="reveal font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-text-muted"
    >
      Where we're starting
    </p>
    <h2
      class="reveal mt-4 text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tighter text-balance"
      style="--reveal-delay: 100ms"
    >
      Built in Amravati.<br />
      <span
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-[#F97316] bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        Open to your city next.
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p
      class="reveal mt-5 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg text-text-secondary text-balance"
      style="--reveal-delay: 200ms"
    >
      We're starting in tier-3 India because that's where most self-taught devs
      are figuring it out alone. The community is online from day one. Your city
      is on the list.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="px-6 pb-16 md:pb-20">
    <CommunityMap client:visible />
  </div>
</section>
